ygData.messageBody:
I know this question has been answered a thousand times, but where would people suggest to move through level 30. I went to High Keep to get 30, but the lines are ridiculous and unlike the other waiting list areas, xp is the only thing there. Any suggestions?

Thanks in advance,
Weiland
<Disciples of Truth>
Erollisi Marr

PS - I got some MM drums this week YEA!!! Only problem is, first thing I did was sail off of a cliff for 200 dmg. This thing really tests your hand-eye coordination =P
